{"tid":1424192,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非同勇武都同我入一入嚟，小妹有野想講","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:01:10.000Z","uid":69472,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4c7786b8d7eb941d226e90f3d58b2a9d149557c7","tid":1424192,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:30:29.000Z","msg":"Sorry唔是小妹，但睇埋落去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋日喺玩左隻驚好好玩，喺一個叫黃大仙既副本打左成日機，發現左幾樣野，有啲反思：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">1. 控煙辦要小隊形式</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n尋日龍翔道有個手足因滅彈，落左單比幾個防暴禁低左嚟打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打左兩個幾月機既你地應該都留意到對家進攻模式，就係tg -&gt; 進攻 <br />\n呢個時候，往往和理非退得極快，勇武上前滅，同扔野還擊，所以和理非同勇武中間就會斷開左，正正係敵家想做到既野，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">想透過tg將人群分開，斷開我地既back up，然後捉落單</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n建議：<br />\n1.1 <br />\n控煙辦要多於1個人，千祈唔好比人落單，最好1-2個滅，1個睇水<br />\n<br />\n1.2<br />\n和理非喺後面可以做咩？你地可以慢慢退，但要留多啲身位，唔駛咁騰雞，食下食下就覺得卡碧仲濃過啲煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好因爲一粒催淚彈而離棄前面既手足，要知道佢地比你吸得更多</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />🚬<br />\n<br />\n準備多啲裝生水既樽，上前為前線補水滅彈，同時睇下邊位前線不適衝過嚟，你一係讓路比佢走，一係扶住佢幫佢洗眼<br />\n<br />\n作為一個氣管差既前線，一衝得都代表真係完全抖唔到氣，啲鼻水口水失禁咁流，試過差啲吸到休克，冇力跑咁濟，但後面啲人慢慢行，逼住撞開你地，小妹真係唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留啲空位比前線真係好重要</span></span></strong>，同時避免人踩人<br />\n<br />\n1.3 <br />\n出左黑旗留意好多人都會開遮，但其實要反左把遮骨成兜狀，先有機會兜住粒彈，正常形狀其實唔太擋到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mkDUWvd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmkDUWvd.png&h=4c62528f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大約好似咁，屈一屈個遮骨成兜狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人記得721上環當晚，信德前出內街，呢啲反骨遮兜左幾粒tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">2. 捨棄三角鐵馬？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n留意到每次出嚟打機，好多玩家都會紮三角鐵欄，可能睇到韓農三角鐵衝擊片段<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWQweh4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWQweh4.gif&h=638246d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但有幾點要注意：一係韓農以三角鐵作「衝擊」之用，但打機既人<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以防守為主，如果唔用嚟「衝擊」，其實訓低啲鐵欄已經係一個路障</span></span></strong>，雖然訓低佢，玩家們想搬都難，佢唔係最好既方法，但想大家一齊集思廣益，諗諗佢<br />\n<br />\n二係紮<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三角鐵馬用左大量人力同物資</span></span></strong>例如索帶，我地應該諗下三角鐵馬作防守呢一招仲係咪適用<br />\n<br />\n建議：<br />\n<br />\n2.1 <br />\n萬一「衝擊」既話，可以試下用<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">菱形鐵馬</span></span></strong>，打直兩個三角鐵推前，威力勁過三角<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/225010_348c584073249feb98b597ca6cb04b33.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F225010_348c584073249feb98b597ca6cb04b33.png&h=9ce4db10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢幅圖係出自一位巴打手筆，但個po一個月前開既，想傾傾整呢種既可能性：<br />\n原po : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216269\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216269</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">3. 光線重要性</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n相信有份打黃大仙副本既朋友都知，對家出人推進之前，會熄左街燈，令到玩家睇唔到催淚彈喺邊，同時難以知道對家去向。<br />\n<br />\n熄燈片： <a href=\"https://streamable.com/er27y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fer27y&d=JGY83BSksxqOTSpEwQoHnSukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=ad9e03ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/er27y</a><br />\n<br />\n建議：<br />\n<br />\n3.1 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一人一電筒</span></span></strong><br />\n小隊形式唔駛我講，互相照應，一人一個電筒，可以照下對方，一熄燈又可以搵路，相信熄燈呢招會繼續玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熟讀地圖真係好重要</span></span></strong>，要靠自己，有啲時候未必有人及時幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\n<br />\n睇返過去呢星期打機發生既事，落單真係好危險，<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無論你地咩位置，都要做好隨時戰鬥既準備，因為形勢愈見凶險，香港人抗爭模式更要進化，唔可以再拘泥於舊有模式，</span></span></ins>祝大家武運昌隆，早日打爆機！"},{"pid":"f7a746b0b5277c5105f689a69c2094b450334e68","tid":1424192,"uid":69472,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:31:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">同場加映，法國仲係好多人零gear去玩，呢度有打機裝備checklist，有咩再補充：</span></span></strong><br />\n最理想梗係每個人都係流動物資first aid站，勿做伸手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n*：optional<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-頭盔/安全帽/電單車盔（有帶最好）<br />\n<br />\n-眼罩（冇窿，最好有反光紙癡住）/泳鏡<br />\n<br />\n-豬咀+濾罐（咪再用n95）<br />\n<br />\n-手套（入門：勞工；高級：3m防割；消防：燒焊手套，最好帶多套隨時比啲磚頭工人/拆欄工人，有時見佢地整到隻手流哂血真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n-面巾（遮耳仔）<br />\n<br />\n-冰袖（遮紋身，遇tg/椒冇咁熱，好過保鮮紙好多）<br />\n<br />\n-黑衫褲鞋（加多件黑色以外既衫）<br />\n<br />\n-鞋套（7仔就有）<br />\n<br />\n-簡單first-aid （鹽水，膠布，粉紅色藥水，紗布）<br />\n<br />\n-水&gt;1支<br />\n<br />\n-電筒<br />\n<br />\n-長遮/行山杖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BJSq3iH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBJSq3iH.gif&h=e65c2312&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重伸，要拮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-*士巴拿/六角匙/wd-40<br />\n<br />\n-*鐵碟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sAfL3qd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsAfL3qd.png&h=f5b6605a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-*油/洗潔精<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5Gn5wp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5Gn5wp.gif&h=a4cb17da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-*laser <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0rzccK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0rzccK.gif&h=8366cba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APkPLBW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPkPLBW.png&h=f760be62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fcd8126b0a4d186800d3dbc0fa929d63c116d89","tid":1424192,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:33:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c70167b097c973b3238eca493a13caeb8992a09","tid":1424192,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b997d9ce21f11b8328980bf7a13aef3841f5909","tid":1424192,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:36:32.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"a8d928ef2db8fc82b075eddde8dc5e73dfbc8621","tid":1424192,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"cf4c5aa5ecf1a6c4763e7c055bd5047ea325bb77","tid":1424192,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:36:52.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"b39898622a8b69b585b979b2f4d20c3e9ccd6abe","tid":1424192,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:37:02.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"61d311cd361eb72bd4abfa5ad205f0c7b0ee462b","tid":1424192,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:37:14.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"7db8d4dd7fce2bfa0dc991f6dd1daacbab9c3919","tid":1424192,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:37:49.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"c960b20bfbd2a7e8385961ebc97c010cdf9eaf51","tid":1424192,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"革"},{"pid":"e4cb2caea52196042170795deedfa014379f2db0","tid":1424192,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:38:24.000Z","msg":"命"},{"pid":"59155483a71debb142a7f3552fa29a7b64149bf5","tid":1424192,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec11365af26685c559eaffd290bb24acffc1c20","tid":1424192,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:43:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d033972a237447434765b70906ab690395212985","tid":1424192,"uid":2607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hk